  "detailed_description": "<strong>Milford Heaven</strong> is a RPG hack 'n' slash game with a top-down view. The city of Milford Heaven is under attack of Luken's monsters, that come from his castle. You, as a warrior, arrive at the town to find out this situation and decide to expore the castle to try to give Luken's reign of terror an end. And, maybe, get some wealth. <br><br>Features: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than a hundred scenarios to explore </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 20 kinds of monsters to fight with </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dozens of itens to collect and use </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Retro art </li></ul>",
